INSERT INTO `event` VALUES (1,0,'Sips Under the Sea: Holidays','<p>Step into a winter wonderland like no other at Georgia Aquarium’s Sips Under the Sea: Holidays, a festive evening crafted exclusively for adults 21 and up. Wander through enchanting underwater galleries adorned with vibrant holiday decor and sparkling lights that add a touch of magic to the season. Whether you arrive in your tackiest sweater or come as you are, get ready to enjoy seasonal cocktails, delicious food, and lively beats provided by AMP’D Entertainment’s live DJ.</p>\r\n<p>Dance, explore, and make holiday memories in an immersive setting where you can toast to the season as you roam through our beautifully illuminated exhibits. This after-hours experience promises to bring a unique and unforgettable twist to your holiday traditions.</p>\r\n<p>Be one of the first 400 guests and receive a specialty holiday mug filled with hot chocolate and the spirit of your choice! Don’t miss out on these exclusive mugs (pictured below). Available while supplies last!</p>\r\n<p>Gather your friends or make it a date night, and dive into the magic of the holidays at Sips Under the Sea: Holidays.</p>','https://i.postimg.cc/Ls5mgCwL/event-sips-under-the-sea-holidays.webp','2024-12-06 19:00:00'),(2,1,'Tuesdays in the Field<br> Time for Taxonomy','<p>The ocean has gone through countless changes over time to resemble the underwater world we have today, and its organisms have adapted to a changing environment too. Join us as we look at modern ocean animals and how they’ve changed compared to their prehistoric relatives. We’ll dig into fossils and explore fascinating adaptations of animals, past and present, as we travel back in time to examine our evolving ocean.</p>','https://i.postimg.cc/RVjrG1k8/event-tuesdays-in-the-field.webp','2024-12-10 09:00:00'),(3,0,'Wellness by the Water Pilates','<p>Break a sweat at the most unique and inspiring fitness studio Atlanta has to offer – Georgia Aquarium.</p>\r\n<p>Wellness by the Water offers a new Pilates class, led by M3 instructors, and designed to challenge students of all experience levels. Sessions take place in our magnificent Oceans Ballroom, offering incredible views of manta rays and whale sharks while you challenge your mind and body. If your fitness goal is to become a happier and healthier version of yourself, this is the session for you.</p>\r\n<p>Doors open at 6:00 pm; class begins at 6:30 pm. Featuring a special Lululemon giveaway at the end of class! All proceeds from Wellness by the Water benefit Georgia Aquarium’s research and conservation initiatives.</p>','https://i.postimg.cc/MKDMQDv7/event-wellness-by-the-water-pilates.jpg','2024-12-10 18:30:00'),(4,0,'A Merry Member Morning','<div>This holiday season, join us in the Ocean’s Ballroom for a magical morning of family fun and holiday cheer! Get ready for a celebration overflowing with festive activities, perfect for creating memories with your loved ones.</div>\r\n<div>Don’t miss this chance to create lasting holiday memories! Reserve your tickets now to be part of our jolly celebration and make this season truly magical with Georgia Aquarium! This event is exclusively available for members of Georgia Aquarium.</div>','https://i.postimg.cc/MGJCJymL/event-a-merry-member-morning.webp','2024-12-15 08:00:00'),(5,0,'Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl Fan Night','<p>Celebrate Bowl Week at this unique football event in Atlanta! Georgia Aquarium is offering football fans the opportunity to be surrounded by millions of gallons of waters, thousands of aquatic animals, and fellow football enthusiasts at Chick-fil-A Peach Bowl Fan Night.</p>\r\n<p>Fans are invited to explore all the Aquarium’s galleries, attend a mini-pep rally. There will be no lack of team spirit at our 5:30pm pep rally that will feature each team’s cheerleaders and mascots. Café and cash bar will be available from 4:00pm – 6:00pm.</p>\r\n<p>Please Note: Sea Lion and Dolphin presentations are not available after 3pm on 12/31/24.</p>','https://i.postimg.cc/nh9XPt3k/event-chick-fil-a-peach-bowl-fan-night.webp','2024-12-31 16:00:00'),(6,0,'New Year Eve Celebration','<p>Join us for an unforgettable night as we ring in 2025 at an exclusive VIP celebration, featuring after-hours access to all aquarium galleries, live DJs, and dance floors that will keep the energy high all night long. Enjoy the lounge in Oceans Ballroom, indulge in gourmet food offerings prepared by Wolfgang Puck Catering, and savor delicious takeaway treats (while supplies last). The premium open bar ensures your glass is always full as you toast to the New Year. Experience the excitement of midnight countdowns in both the atrium and ballroom, surrounded by breathtaking aquatic views.</p>\r\n<p>Your celebration goes beyond the party—proceeds from our New Year’s Eve event support vital ocean conservation efforts, helping us protect marine life.</p>\r\n<p>Tickets are limited and expected to sell out quickly, so secure yours soon!</p>','https://i.postimg.cc/qvcx5nbQ/event-new-year-s-eve-celebration.webp','2024-12-31 21:00:00'),(7,1,'Tuesdays in the Field<br> All Hands on Deck','<p>All hands on deck! Do you think you have what it takes to work with animals? Maybe you want to work in a lab, design a habitat, or even manage animal diets. It takes a boatload of people to keep Georgia Aquarium afloat, so come explore the many different career opportunities and learn a little more about all the behind-the-seas work happening every day.</p>','https://i.postimg.cc/RVjrG1k8/event-tuesdays-in-the-field.webp','2025-01-14 09:00:00'),(8,1,'Tuesdays in the Field<br> Seeds of Sustainability','<p>Ready to grow a new, sustainable habit in this new year? Discover how to be an environmental superhero this Tuesday in the Field with February’s Seeds of Sustainability. From ocean clean-up strategies to cultivating native plants, we’ll dig into how we can support the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals and take care of this beautiful planet that we call home.<p>','https://i.postimg.cc/RVjrG1k8/event-tuesdays-in-the-field.webp','2025-02-11 09:00:00');
